<http://www.spektrix.com/darkehallsociety/event/27601AQVLTVTCJRHPTLCPRBPBJCDTNLPC>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Conservatory Musical Theatre Showcase - DAY 4";
  schema:description """
	Get ready for four days of singing, dancing, and performing at the <span class=\"BoldText\">Conservatory Musical Theatre Showcase</span>. Students from the University of Regina Conservatory of Performing Arts’ youth musical theatre programs are sure to dazzle and delight the audience with their triple threat status.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Performances on <span class=\"BoldText\">DAY 4</span> will include the following (in performance order):<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Mini Glee (5:00pm class & 5:50pm class)</span> presents choral music for <span class=\"BoldText\">Songs of a Disney Hero and Sidekick</span>. Each group will perform individually then will present a special joint song. This group is directed by Fallon Hantelman-Stewart with support from Yzabelle Lopez.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Junior Glee (Wednesday, 6:30pm class)</span> presents choral music from <span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Oliver!</span></span>  These groups are directed by Wren Magalong with support from Aubrey Mutala.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Junior Glee (5:15pm class & 6:30pm class)</span> presents choral music from <span class=\"BoldText\">Disney’s Encanto and Moana</span>. Each group will perform individually then will present a special joint song for the finale. These groups are directed by Katherine Mutschler with support from Jenah Healy.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>There will be a short transition break between each class just to reset the stage and coordinate students.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Learn more about the University of Regina Conservatory of Performing Arts and about joining Summer Creative Camps in July & August or our Musical Theatre & Drama programs in the fall of 2026:  <span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.uregina.ca/academics/continuing-education/conservatory-of-performing-arts.html\"> Conservatory of Performing Arts</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Tickets are $8.40 in advance and $10.50 at the door, inclusive of fees and taxes.  Seating is not assigned.</span>
""";
