<http://www.spektrix.com/darkehallsociety/event/39601AJRRLKSVBMNJSKBSJSPPVNLVSKDK>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Nachda Punjab 2026";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">Nachda Punjab 2026</span> is a vibrant cultural festival dedicated to showcasing the skills, passion, and spirit of young performers and emerging leaders. Through energetic Bhangra and traditional dance forms, participants express not only their talent but also their journey of growth, discipline, and learning. Each performance reflects dedication, teamwork, and a deep connection to Punjabi heritage.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>With lively music, colorful costumes, and electrifying stage presence, the festival brings the true essence of Punjab to life. It serves as a platform where youth build confidence, develop leadership, and celebrate their cultural identity. More than just a competition, Nachda Punjab 2026 inspires creativity, unity, and excellence, encouraging the next generation to carry forward traditions with pride while embracing new heights of achievement.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Tickets are $25 inclusive of fees and taxes.  Children under 5 years are free but do require a ticket.  Seating is not assigned.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All sales are final; no refunds issued.</span>
""";
