<http://www.spektrix.com/darkehallsociety/event/20401AHPLRCCNVVRTBBQTNVLNPCCJVRGB>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Regina Musical Club Organ Series - Lost in the Wind: Valerie Hall, Organ & Dean McNeill, Trumpet";
  schema:description """
	The organ series rounds out with Saskatchewan musicians in an exploration of wind-powered sound. <span class=\"BoldText\">Dean McNeill</span>, professor of Jazz and Trumpet at The University of Saskatchewan joins <span class=\"BoldText\">Valerie Hall</span>, touring concert organist based in Regina, for an unforgettable evening of music for trumpet and organ. This will not be the music you heard at your best friend’s wedding!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">This show is taking place at Knox Metropolitan Church. 2340 Victoria Avenue.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Tickets are $40 for adults, $35 for seniors, inclusive of fees and taxes. Student tickets are available for free at the door (with Student ID). Seating is not assigned.</span>
""";
