<http://www.spektrix.com/darkehallsociety/event/39201APPPJQSCBDBPCLLVKSNCLNHTDTRQ>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Great Dance Academy Heist";
  schema:description """
	Step into a world of sparkle, mystery, and movement at <span class=\"BoldText\">3S Dance Co.’s “The Great Dance Academy Heist.”</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This year’s recital celebrates the passion, growth, and dedication of our incredible dancers of all ages. From our tiniest stars to our seasoned performers, each dancer takes the stage to showcase the hard work, confidence, and creativity they’ve built all season long.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>But this is no ordinary recital… <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>When a priceless gem suddenly vanishes, the stage transforms into an exciting journey filled with energy, suspense, and unforgettable performances. Our dancers must work together to follow the clues, overcome challenges, and bring the stolen gem back where it belongs.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Join us for an evening that celebrates talent, teamwork, and the beauty of dance—we can’t wait to share this adventure with you! <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Tickets are $10 inclusive of fees and taxes.  Seating is not assigned.</span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-06-18T19:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
